    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously preserved and presenting in absolute mint condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, every detail has been curated for the most discerning driver. Mechanically unrivaled and aesthetically impeccable, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that performs as perfectly as it looks. A true investment-grade offering for those who demand nothing less than the best.",
      "price": 48500.0,
