    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine yourself behind the wheel of this automotive poem, where every curve of the bodywork captures the golden hour light like a polished jewel. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine that transports you to a more elegant era. The engine hums with a soulful, rhythmic cadence, a mechanical symphony that speaks of open roads and endless horizons. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the rich, comforting scent of heritage leather and the cool touch of chrome accents that have been preserved with a curator's devotion. This vehicle has been cherished, not just owned, standing as a pristine testament to a time when craftsmanship was king. To drive it is to command respect; to own it is to hold a piece of history in its most glorious form.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
